The '''Lucre Cosminational Bank''' was a [[Bank/Legends|bank]] located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Mazuma]]. After being tipped off about a deal between [[Millennium Astro-Engineering]] and the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]],
[[Alliance Starfighter Corps/Legends|Rebel Fighter Command]] left 200,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] at the bank for [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]].<ref name="The Flight of the Falcon" />

